{"tid":149104,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"擺脫18 歲嬰兒肥劇照鄉土味 「小丑女」蛻變成全球性感女神！","createTime":"2017-03-09T04:45:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T09:43:45.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d91086f187529d3d6040a82d9f44796864b129f9","tid":149104,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T04:45:06.000Z","msg":"26 歲澳洲女演員女演員Margot Robbie去年以 DC 超級英雄大作《自殺突擊隊》（Suicide Squad )當中的超級英雄角色「小丑女」哈莉&middot;奎茵（Harley Quinn）走紅全球，現在「瑪格羅比」這個名字已經成為全球的性感女神。現在又確定她將會出演索尼的新作品《羅賓漢》（Robin Hood），飾演女主角瑪莉安（Marian）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63384/58be126443352.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63384%2F58be126443352.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=4e64c2a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藉此同時媒體也回顧了瑪格羅比如何從一位澳洲肥皂劇的無名演員，逐步變成炙手可熱的好萊塢明日之星，不過令網友感到驚訝的是，當年 18 歲的瑪格羅比在劇中居然比現在還顯老！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63384/58be1294e6222.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63384%2F58be1294e6222.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=490cb26b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來澳洲肥皂劇《鄰居》（Neighbours）是瑪格羅比出道的戲劇作品，2008 年她當時只是前來客串一下的小角色，後來成為了常駐角色，逐漸打開知名度。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63384/58be1268e9a65.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63384%2F58be1268e9a65.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=90bd9f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當時還有一點嬰兒肥的瑪格羅比完全不顧形象搞笑，沒有人知道這位女演員未來會在好萊塢以「小丑女」掀起全球 Cosplay 旋風。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1063/1063378.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1063%2F1063378.jpg&h=3283e70f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63384/58be126b83dc7.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63384%2F58be126b83dc7.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=44db798d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼瑪格羅比當時在戲劇中的服裝也充滿了「孕婦裝感」，像是碎花雪紡紗長裙搭配牛仔褲，牛仔褲還塞進長靴裡，真的相當有「鄉土味」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63384/58be13b3ad758.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63384%2F58be13b3ad758.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=33d2c893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼這可不完全是造型師的錯，瑪格羅比早期出席活動的穿搭都偏向這種風格。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63384/58be126d0206e.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63384%2F58be126d0206e.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=d5204af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼這更讓人感受到瑪格羅比在 5 年後出演《華爾街之狼》（Wolf Of Wall Street），體型和服裝搭配上已經歷過不小的變化。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63384/58be12697abc5.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63384%2F58be12697abc5.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=da286097&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過別擔心，現在我們還是有機會看到瑪格羅比「暴肥」的模樣，原因就是在她主演的新傳記電影《 I, Tonya 》中，她將會飾演發福的花式溜冰選手坦雅哈丁 ( Tonya Harding ) ，許多網友都對於擁有頂級美女封號的瑪格羅比來說，願意為戲增肥堪稱是非常敬業，也為這部傳記電影增加了看頭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/63384/58be1320edabf.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F63384%2F58be1320edabf.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=149e8ef6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c26e8fc37819a40f0807c253f82f186838ecd8f","tid":149104,"uid":90123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:32:44.000Z","msg":"美極呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc277f1d3b01ef3bdaa4b2786b7a4c77b9e4831c","tid":149104,"uid":3822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T09:43:45.000Z","msg":"好似兩個人咁"}]}